The paper focuses on using computer vision techniques, specifically convolutional neural networks, for analyzing laparoscopic surgery videos. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories. The paper also discusses unsupervised learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper mentions video indexing and annotation, which are tasks in multimedia (cs.MM).
